BASIC STEPS TO IMPLEMENT MAD LAB: 

1.  Create a new Android project 

Go to D drive -> MAD folder -> adt bundle -> eclipse -> click eclipse purple color ball icon -> select workspace - >  java adt -> file -> new -> android application -> application name -> next -> finish 

2.Editing code 

Goto app folder -> src -> java-> MainActivity.java 

For XML codes : goto res folder -> layout -> activity_main.xml

3.To run 

Goto menu bar (in top) -> AVD -> device definition -> select any one of the phone (emulator) -> create AVD -> click ok 

Now in the menubar -> click run as Android application option or use play button to run the app
